; NAME: gpi_create_2d_low_frequency_flat
; PIPELINE PRIMITIVE DESCRIPTION: Create 2D Low Frequency Flat
; 
; /!\ PROBABLY OUT OF DATE /!\ /!\ PROBABLY OUT OF DATE /!\ 
